About this item

  • The smart hub of your homeSets your hands freeEnjoy a brand new intelligent life by controlling smart devices in your home through intelligent voice assistant.
  • Now you can use different voice commands to control the smart speaker. To play music, find out the weather, stay tuned to the latest news or turn up/down the volume, all you need to say is "Ok Google".
  • IR controlA voice remote control for home appliancesThe built-in IR transmitter module combined with Google Assistant can achieve voice control of home appliances when you are in the room, infusing new life into conventional non-smart devices*.
  • Perfectly balanced sound fieldThe increased capacity, the all-side speaker cone, and the innovative cavity design all contribute to the richness and details of the sound, creating a perfectly balanced sound field for great sound from all angles.
  • It just takes two to form a stereo. Why not have a family concert?Combine two devices of the same model to form a stereo, and you can instantly enjoy an immersive experience. Indulge yourself in the sonorous stereo sound field freely*.
  • Seamless connection for a home-wide smart sound fieldNo matter how big your home is, you don't need to worry. Multiple smart speakers* can be connected together for home-wide synchronous playing and even for hands-free calls with Google Duo*. Voice commands are even easier. Your commands will be responded to at any time, making your home life freer.
  • Buttons : Play/Pause, Volume up, Volume down, Mute Microphone Array 2Mics, with far field voice wake up sopport Speaker 1.5" full-range speaker LightOne-Dot LED light Connectivity802.11a/b/g/n/ac, 2.4GHz/5GHz | Bluetooth 5.0 |

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
